### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### List Events
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/events

###

### Get Single Event (replace with real ID from seed)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}

###

### Create Booking — Single Event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "ambra@example.com",
  "items": [
    { "eventId": "{{eventId}}", "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

###

### Create Booking — Multi-Event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "ambra@example.com",
  "items": [
    { "eventId": "{{eventId1}}", "quantity": 3 },
    { "eventId": "{{eventId2}}", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

###

### Create Booking — Should FAIL (quantity > 3)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "fail@example.com",
  "items": [
    { "eventId": "{{eventId}}", "quantity": 4 }
  ]
}

###

### List Bookings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bookings

###

### List Bookings — Filter by email
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bookings?email=ambra@example.com

###

### Get Single Booking
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bookings/{{bookingId}}

###

### Cancel Booking
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel

